@startuml Sequence Diagram – Online Shopping System

actor Customer
participant Cart
participant PaymentService
participant OrderService

== Adding items to cart ==
Customer -> Cart: addItem(productId, quantity)
Cart --> Customer: itemAddedConfirmation

== Proceed to checkout ==
Customer -> Cart: checkout()
Cart -> PaymentService: makePayment(amount)
activate PaymentService

PaymentService --> Cart: paymentStatus(success)
deactivate PaymentService

== Order confirmation ==
Cart -> OrderService: createOrder(cartDetails)
activate OrderService
OrderService --> Cart: orderConfirmed(orderId)
deactivate OrderService

Cart --> Customer: displayOrderConfirmation(orderId)

@enduml
